27
00:02:41,874 --> 00:02:44,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait, Ninomiya's EK9 is comin' from the rear?!</b></font>

28
00:02:44,744 --> 00:02:48,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he'd gone in front, the race prob'ly
